---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Prose from '../components/Prose.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy — CosmoCrew"
  description="How the CosmoCrew website handles your data — the short version: it doesn't. No cookies, no analytics, no tracking."
  path="privacy"
>
  <section class="container narrow">
    <div class="section-head">
      <p class="eyebrow">Privacy</p>
      <h1>Privacy</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        How this website handles your data — the short version: it doesn&rsquo;t.
      </p>
    </div>

    <Prose>
      <p><em>Last updated: 28 June 2026</em></p>

      <p>
        This policy covers the CosmoCrew website (<strong>cosmocrew.dev</strong> and
        its GitHub Pages address). For the apps themselves, see <em>Our apps</em> below.
      </p>

      <h2>What we collect</h2>
      <p>
        Nothing. This is a static website. It sets no cookies, runs no analytics,
        and contains no advertising or third-party trackers. We don&rsquo;t ask
        for, collect, or store any personal information through this site.
      </p>

      <h2>Hosting</h2>
      <p>
        The site is hosted on <strong>GitHub Pages</strong>. Like any web host,
        GitHub may process standard technical information (such as your IP address
        and browser request data) in order to deliver the site and protect its
        service. That processing is governed by <a href="https://docs.github.com/en/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-privacy-statement" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">GitHub&rsquo;s Privacy Statement</a>.
        We add no tracking of our own on top of it.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        If you email us at <a href="mailto:contact@cosmocrew.dev">contact@cosmocrew.dev</a>,
        we receive your message and email address (routed to our inbox via
        Cloudflare Email Routing) and use them only to reply. We don&rsquo;t add
        you to any mailing list.
      </p>

      <h2>Our apps</h2>
      <p>
        The CosmoCrew apps are separate from this website. Each app&rsquo;s data
        practices are described in its App Store privacy details and on its
        support page:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>SliceFocus</strong> — <a href="https://slicefocus.app" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">slicefocus.app</a></li>
        <li><strong>LexiPower</strong> — <a href="https://anunnakicosmocrew.github.io/lexipower-support/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">support page</a></li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Changes</h2>
      <p>
        If this policy changes, we&rsquo;ll update the date at the top of this page.
      </p>
    </Prose>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .narrow {
    max-width: var(--maxw-prose);
  }
</style>
